data.name: lblWhatsThis.ToolTip
data.value:
These are Optional fields. Type in your AD domain for the default domain and then your "replace domain" is your Gsuite address.
This will allow the program to automatically change your userbase from user@Default.xyz to user@Gsuite.xyz for LDAP convenience.
Typically used for instances where you'd want TTO's GSuite backup tool to automatically do the work for you when it comes to mirror'ing what you would expect to see from your GSuite admin console. Go ahead, give it a try!
